    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"moving forward.\" there's no version of my life where I'm not looking at this wreckage every single day. the debt is a mountain, and the shame is even bigger. it feels like I'm just trapped in this loop of misery. sometimes i think the only way to actually stop the noise and the feeling of being a failure is to just... make it stop. for good. to just find a way to exit this before it gets even worse.",
